text: Douglass USD 396 is a public unified school district headquartered in Douglass, Kansas, United States. The district includes the community of Douglass and nearby rural areas. ==Schools== The school district operates the following schools: * Douglass High School * Sisk Middle School * Seal Elementary School ==See also== * Kansas State Department of Education * Kansas State High School Activities Association * List of high schools in Kansas * List of unified school districts in Kansas ==References== ==External links== * Category:School districts in Kansas
